***************************************************************************
* Supervisory file for SOCSIM microsimulation for Norway 1967-2022
* Created on 05.02.2024 by Bettina Huenteler
***************************************************************************
* This simulation uses as input age-specific data retrieved from 
* the Human Fertility Database (HFD) and the Human Mortality Database (HMD) 
* converted into SOCSIM format.
***************************************************************************
segments 178  
input_file presim

bint 12
hetfert 0
marriage_queues 1
marriage_eval distribution
marriage_after_childbirth 1 
random_father 0

***********************************************************************
* Pre-simulation (100 years) to get stable population at 31-12-1845 
* Using HFC rates for 1846 - 1966 
* and HMD rates for 1967 - 2022 (already in one file)

duration 1200
include rates/NORfert1846
include rates/NORmort1846
run

* First simulation with actual mortality rates. 
* Give population at 31-12-1846

